data.description: Welcome to your new dream home in Powder Springs, Georgia! This stunning cul-de-sac residence, born out of an unexpected job transfer, invites you to seize the opportunity as the HIGHLY MOTIVATED SELLER presents this exquisite property to the market. Discover the allure of the covered back patio; a haven for casual get-togethers and entertaining. The fenced backyard ensures privacy, providing a tranquil area for relaxation. Inside, the formal dining room welcomes you with subtle elegance, boasting coffered ceilings and judges paneling, adorned with chair rail molding and crown molding is a true testament to the home's meticulous craftsmanship. The heart of this home is a dynamic blend of open living spaces, a cozy yet spacious family room with a fireplace, and a kitchen that's as stylish as it is functional. Granite countertops, 52" cabinets, and an oversized island set the stage for culinary creativity, seamlessly connecting with the well appointed breakfast area. As you ascend to the Upper Level, you are greeted by an Oversized Loft and three additional Guest Bedrooms. The Master Bedroom, a sanctuary in itself, boasts a spacious Sitting Area and a Fireplace that adds an extra touch of warmth and ambiance to your personal retreat. This home is situated in a vibrant Swim and Tennis community, just a short drive from Downtown Powder Springs, C. H. James Pkwy., Richard D. Sailors Pkwy., vibrant Shopping Districts, Dining Venues, and the new Powder Springs Amphitheater. Embrace the lifestyle you deserve. Schedule a viewing today and make this remarkable property your forever home! Make an OFFER TODAY - Receive a RESPONSE in HOURS. SELLER SAY'S, "SELL!!!! For more information, feel free to contact Kelly Aguebor @ 404-914-8324 (Please Text for a quicker response) or Travis King @ 404-391-5373.
